<emphasis id="2FE6EAC40E562D2BFECCA426BF30DB50" bold="true" box="[262,323,1293,1317]" pageId="16" pageNumber="1272">Note:</emphasis>
In the original description, 
<bibRefCitation id="79034B270E562D2BFDB0A426BD4DDB50" author="Bernhauer M" box="[634,830,1293,1317]" pageId="16" pageNumber="1272" pagination="49 - 53" refId="ref12682" refString="Bernhauer M. 1917. Neue Arten der Gattungen Piestus, Leptochirus und Conosoma aus Sudamerika. Neue Beitr Syst Insektenk. 1: 45 - 48, 49 - 53." type="journal article" year="1917">Bernhauer (1917)</bibRefCitation>
